description: Amendments to approved scheme 01/00877/FUL (Redevelopment of site, involving the demolition of existing buildings and erection of part 3, 4 and 6 storey buildings for retail, offices and 90 self contained flats and 6 houses), granted by appeal on 13/12/2001, with respect to reduction from dual ramp access to underground parking to single ramp, alterations to the Clapham Road access and enlargement of the outbuilding housing the electricity sub station, refuse storage and lift lobby.
